{"tid":2312259,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–火星的氧氣供應問題","createTime":"2020-12-04T17:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T14:46:12.000Z","uid":38861,"like":69,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"2dfe6638657079d947f3897b5b76e2952e73aaad","tid":2312259,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T17:46:28.000Z","msg":"NASA計劃2033年派人類登陸火星，而火星大氣的氧含量只有0.14%，不足生存用，因此氧氣的供應問題必須著手解決。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DyjSk4O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyjSk4O.jpg&h=b9943b0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）為針對此問題，NASA與MIT攜手合作，推行命為MOXIE (Mars OXygen In situ resource utilization Experiment) 的方案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9fVqF4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9fVqF4T.jpg&h=23d76375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n理論就是將火星的二氧化碳電解成為可呼吸用的氧氣及一氧化碳，箇中所產生的一氧化碳對人體有效，所以必須隔走。<br />\n而2020的火星登陸計劃其中一項試驗，就是測試裝置能否達到每小時產生10-22克氧氣的功效。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）另一方面，根據早前鳳凰號登陸器所得出的資料，火星的水份含有大量的Mg(ClO4)2 化學物，Mg(ClO4)2 將水份的結冰點降低，促使水份在攝氏零下70度才會結冰。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/auick4W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fauick4W.jpg&h=9a432736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n火星的年度平均溫度為攝氏零下63度，上下幅度為攝氏100度，所以水份亦會有部份時間呈液體狀態。<br />\n<br />\n有科學家嘗試運用攝氏零下36度模擬火星情景(Ref1)，成功將水化解成氧氣(呼吸用)及氫氣(燃料用)，不但不會產生有毒的二氧化碳，而且功率比NASA方法高出5倍有多。<br />\n<br />\n雖然無法確定此理論是否真的在火星可行，但這項研究至少為2033年登陸火星的行動提供另一道製氧及燃料的方案。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w%2BEzQ5hKls32m7Ak2FFrcx0%3D&h=83fab290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.pnas.org/content/early/2020/11/24/2008613117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnas.org%2Fcontent%2Fearly%2F2020%2F11%2F24%2F2008613117&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w%2BEzQ5hKls32m7Ak2FFrcx0%3D&h=cf7c6576\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pnas.org/content/early/2020/11/24/2008613117</a>"},{"pid":"04d3f1a06163e45a209a8bf9f08b07ad36a596b2","tid":2312259,"uid":364233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T17:48:43.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac43fb23f22298477c1425622393e6248a9133a","tid":2312259,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T17:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a2bd8590003ae10e14805ef8e35cab6ddcf2c2","tid":2312259,"uid":366544,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T17:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb19fae5ed66c3e6566cc2622b2f5d1670f3aab4","tid":2312259,"uid":294,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T17:50:51.000Z","msg":"可以增加火星d 氧氣<br />\n<br />\n點解全球暖化又解決唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a85f15c70b3c61171715a8fc4c436e42f959b6","tid":2312259,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T17:52:01.000Z","msg":"寫得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a17a101813138e19a89e8d461f15e5c5edbeba","tid":2312259,"uid":233873,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T17:55:54.000Z","msg":"點解唔放幾隻蟑螂上火星？"},{"pid":"494db49a429125f1dc746e6c567ad755d0b7787d","tid":2312259,"uid":38861,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"cb19fae5ed66c3e6566cc2622b2f5d167